Required programs:

soundtouch
lame
mplayer
youtube-dl (python lib), tested with version 2014.01.30.2
mediainfo
mpg123 (for flv videos)
faad2 (for mp4 videos)
elasticsearch

elasticsearch-analysis-morphology (optional)
installation:
$ cd /usr/share/elasticsearch
$ sudo -u elasticsearch bin/plugin -install analysis-morphology -url http://dl.bintray.com/content/imotov/elasticsearch-plugins/elasticsearch-analysis-morphology-1.1.0.zip
